name: NooksMarketplace
description: A web app I created that supplements user gameplay for the Nintendo game app, Animal Crossing: Pocket Camp. I saw a struggle in trading items due to players only being allowed to trade within their friends list, and their friends will not always have the items that are desired. This web app solves the problem by allowing users to all get together and declare what items they are buying/selling, and at what quantity. Afterwards, they also provide their ID in order for someone who meets their needs can add them.
